==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Frory
<hw>Fro"ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>fre⟦oacute⟧rig</ets>. See <er>Frorn</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Frozen; stiff with cold.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Covered with a froth like hoarfrost.</def>
<mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The foaming steed with <qex>frory</qex> bit to steer.</q>
<rj><qau>Fairfax.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>frosh</ent>⟦br⟧
